HEADWORD: Freezer
<hw>Freez"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, cools or freezes, as a refrigerator, or the tub and can used in
the process of freezing ice cream.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

